{
  "texts": [
    "FiltPoss is the category of filter-descriptive possibility frames with p-morphisms.Theorem 5.41 (Dual Equivalence II).",
    "BAO is dually equivalent to Filt-Poss.",
    "Reflection with Filter-Descriptive FramesNext we observe that FiltPoss is a full subcategory of the category Poss of possibility frames with possibility morphisms.Proposition 5.42 (Full Subcategory II).",
    "Every possibility morphism between filter-descriptive possibility frames is a p-morphism.Proof.",
    "Immediate from Theorems 5.34.1 and 5.40.In fact, we will show that FiltPoss is a reflective subcategory of Poss."
  ]
}